data.description:
Looking for a first time starter home or an investment this maybe the home for you !
This home has approx. 1386 sq. ft. 4 Bedrooms and 2 Baths.
Nice Living Room with built ins and Dining Room open to kitchen with Refrigerator AS-IS, Stove and Dishwasher.
Place for washer and dryer.
Washer stays AS-IS.
There is also a guest house that is approx.483 sq. ft. that has a Living Room kitchen combo. with bedroom and bath .
Place for a washer and dryer.
This could be rented out separate from the main house.
The home is across the street from First Baptist and within walking distance of Minden Medical.
